trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Windows.Input.CommandBinding"></xref> objects.
All objects which derive from <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> have a CommandBindingCollection named <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.CommandBindings%2A>.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Input.CommandBindingCollection"></xref> class.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Input.CommandBindingCollection"></xref> class using the items in the specified <xref:System.Collections.IList>.
The collection whose items are copied to the new <xref href="System.Windows.Input.CommandBindingCollection"></xref>.
Adds the specified <xref href="System.Windows.Input.CommandBinding"></xref> to this <xref href="System.Windows.Input.CommandBindingCollection"></xref>.
The binding to add to the collection.
0, if the operation was successful (note that this is not the index of the added item).
commandBinding is **null**.

**true** if the specified <xref href="System.Windows.Input.CommandBinding"></xref> is in the collection; otherwise, **false**.
Copies all of the items in the <xref href="System.Windows.Input.CommandBindingCollection"></xref> to the specified one-dimensional array, starting at the specified index of the target array.
The array into which the collection is copied.
The index position in `commandBindings` at which copying starts.

Gets a value indicating whether this <xref href="System.Windows.Input.CommandBindingCollection"></xref> has a fixed size.
A <xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandBindingCollection> is never a fixed size; therefore, IsFixedSize will always return **false**.
**true** if the collection has a fixed size; otherwise, **false**.
The default value is **false**.
Gets a value indicating whether this <xref href="System.Windows.Input.CommandBindingCollection"></xref> is read-only.
A <xref:System.Windows.Input.CommandBindingCollection> is never read-only; therefore, IsReadOnly will always return `false`.
<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the collection is read-only; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
